on) | | |- | בלה | blh | Balah | {{Strong-number|H1088|H|1088}} | Joshua 19:3 | 1 | Simeon within Judah | | = Baalah (H1173) ? |- | במות בעל, במות | bmwt bʿl, bmwt | [[Bamoth-Baal]], Bamoth | {{Strong-number|H1120|H|1120}} | Joshua 13:17 | 4 | Reuben (east of Jordan) | | |- | בניברק | bnybrq | Bene-Berak | {{Strong-number|H1139|H|1139}} | Joshua 19:45 | 1 | Dan | | |- | בעל גד | bʿl gd | Baal-Gad | {{Strong-number|H1171|H|1171}} | Joshua 11:17; 12:7; 13:5 | 3 | Manasseh?, Naphtali? (in the valley of Lebanon under Mount Hermon, on the west side of the Jordan river) | | |- | בעלה | bʿlh | Baalah [of Judah 1] | {{Strong-number|H1173|H|1173}} | Joshua 15:9.10 | 3 | Judah (northern border between Jerusalem and Beth-Shemesh) | see Kiriath-Jearim (H7157) | = Kiriath-Jearim (H7157) |- | בעלה | bʿlh | Baalah [of Judah 2] | {{Strong-number|H1173|H|1173}} | Joshua 15:29 | 1 | Judah (southwestern territory bordering Edom; group A, important cities: Beersheba, Hormah, Ziklag) | | = Balah (H1088, Simeon's) ? |- | בעלות | bʿlwt | Bealoth | {{Strong-number|H1175|H|1175}} | Joshua 15:24 | 2 or 1 | Judah (southwestern territory bordering Edom; group A, important cities: Beersheba, Hormah, Ziklag) | | |- | בעלת | bʿlt | Baalath | {{Strong-number|H1191|H|1191}} | Joshua 19:44 | 3 | Dan | | |- | בעלת באר | bʿlt bʾr | Baalath-Beer | {{Strong-number|H1192|H|1192}} | Joshua 19:8 | 1 | Simeon (within Judah?, in the Negev?) | | |- | בעשתרה | bʿštrh | Beesh-Terah | {{Strong-number|H1203|H|1203}} | Joshua 21:27 | 1 | Manasseh (east of the Jordan river; a levitical city) | | |- | בצקת | bṣqt | Bozkath | {{Strong-number|H1218|H|1218}} | Joshua 15:39 | 2 | Judah (important cities: Lachish, Eglon, Makkedah) | | |- | בצר | bṣr | [[Bezer]] | {{Strong-number|H1221|H|1221}} | Joshua 20:8; 21:36 | 4 | Reuben (on the east side of the Jordan; not far from Jericho?; a city of refuge; a levitical city) | | |- | בתול | btwl | Bethul | {{Strong-number|H1329|H|1329}} | Joshua 19:4 | 1 | Simeon within Judah (l